System Architecture

The FitHub CRM system is built using the Salesforce Lightning Platform. The application uses custom objects, relationships, automation, and analytics features provided by Salesforce.

Objects Created:

Member
Trainer
Class
Booking

Relationships:

Member → Booking (Master-Detail)
Class → Booking (Master-Detail)
Trainer → Class (Lookup)

Automation Implemented:

Formula fields to determine membership status and class availability
Validation rules to ensure correct data entry
Flow automation for sending notifications

Analytics:
Reports and dashboards are used to analyze class bookings, revenue, and attendance.
